data.comment: Get-ChildItem -Path $env:TEMP\checkoutuow | ForEach-Object -Begin { $checkoutItems = [System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary[string,string[]]]::new() } -Process { $checkout = ($_ | Select-String -Pattern "([^\s\)\(]+)(?=.*\(checkout\))").Matches.Value | Sort-Object -Unique; $elements = ($_.BaseName | Select-String -Pattern '[^\s\(\)]+' -AllMatches).Matches.Value; $elements | ForEach-Object { $checkoutItems.Add($_,$checkout); } } -End { $checkoutItems } | Export-Clixml -Path $env:OneDriveCommercial\checkoutUowItems.xml $checkoutItemsPerProgram = [System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary[string,hashtable]]::new() $checkoutItemsPerProgram['B_IFM'] = $checkoutItems

$CsdbProgram = 'GXPROD', 'CTALPROD', 'B_IFM', 'CH604PROD', 'LJ4045PROD' $query = @" SELECT DISTINCT o.objectname AS Name, docnbr.attributevalue AS Docnbr, manual.attributevalue AS Manual FROM objectnew o, objectattribute docnbr, objectattribute manual WHERE o.objectref = docnbr.objectref AND manual.objectref = o.objectref AND docnbr.attributename = 'DOCNBR' AND manual.attributename = 'MANUAL' ORDER BY docnbr.attributevalue "@ foreach($Program in $CsdbProgram){ $manualFromDocnbr = [System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary[string,string]]::new() $DbProgram = $dbConnections.connections.info.serviceName | Where-Object -FilterScript { $_ -match ($program -replace '_').Substring(0, 2) } | Select-Object -First 1 $sqlClOut = Write-Output "SET SQLFORMAT JSON`n$query" | SQLcl -S "***REMOVED***/${DbProgram}" | Join-String -Separator "`r`n"; if ([string]::IsNullOrEmpty($sqlClOut)) { Write-Warning -Message "No data found for 'IFM' with docnbr '$docnbr' in 'B_IFM'" }; try { $splitOut = $sqlClOut | Select-String -Pattern '(?ms)(?<json>{.*})(?<err>.*)'; $jsonPart = $splitOut.Matches.Groups | Where-Object -Property Name -EQ 'json' | Select-Object -ExpandProperty Value; $errPart = $splitOut.Matches.Groups | Where-Object -Property Name -EQ 'err' | ForEach-Object { $_.Value.Trim() }; $sqlClObj = $jsonPart | ConvertFrom-Json; $VerboseMessage = "JSON part: $sqlClObj"; if ($null -eq $sqlClObj -and $null -ne $errPart) { Write-Warning -Message $errPart }else { $VerboseMessage = "SQLcl output: $sqlClOut" } } catch { Write-Warning -Message "Malformed query result for 'IFM' with docnbr '$docnbr' in 'B_IFM'" }; if ($null -ne $sqlClObj.results -and $null -ne $sqlClObj.results.items -and $null -ne $sqlClObj.results.items.manual) { $sqlClObj.results.items | ForEach-Object { $manualFromDocnbr.Add($_.docnbr,$_.manual) } } $docnbrManualFromProgram.Add($Program,$manualFromDocnbr) } $query = @" SELECT DISTINCT o.objectname AS Name, docnbr.attributevalue AS Docnbr, manual.attributevalue AS Manual FROM objectnew o, objectattribute docnbr, objectattribute manual WHERE o.objectref = docnbr.objectref AND manual.objectref = o.objectref AND docnbr.attributename = 'DOCNBR' AND manual.attributename = 'MANUALTYPE' ORDER BY docnbr.attributevalue "@ foreach($Program in 'GXPROD','CH604PROD','CTALPROD','LJ4045PROD'){
$DbProgram = $dbConnections.connections.info.serviceName | Where-Object -FilterScript { $_ -match ($program -replace '_').Substring(0, 2) } | Select-Object -First 1 $sqlClOut = Write-Output "SET SQLFORMAT JSON`n$query" | SQLcl -S "***REMOVED***/${DbProgram}" | Join-String -Separator "`r`n"; if ([string]::IsNullOrEmpty($sqlClOut)) { Write-Warning -Message "No data found for 'IFM' with docnbr '$docnbr' in 'B_IFM'" }; try { $splitOut = $sqlClOut | Select-String -Pattern '(?ms)(?<json>{.*})(?<err>.*)'; $jsonPart = $splitOut.Matches.Groups | Where-Object -Property Name -EQ 'json' | Select-Object -ExpandProperty Value; $errPart = $splitOut.Matches.Groups | Where-Object -Property Name -EQ 'err' | ForEach-Object { $_.Value.Trim() }; $sqlClObj = $jsonPart | ConvertFrom-Json; $VerboseMessage = "JSON part: $sqlClObj"; if ($null -eq $sqlClObj -and $null -ne $errPart) { Write-Warning -Message $errPart }else { $VerboseMessage = "SQLcl output: $sqlClOut" } } catch { Write-Warning -Message "Malformed query result for 'IFM' with docnbr '$docnbr' in 'B_IFM'" }; if ($null -ne $sqlClObj.results -and $null -ne $sqlClObj.results.items -and $null -ne $sqlClObj.results.items.manual) { $sqlClObj.results.items | ForEach-Object { if(-not $docnbrManualFromProgram[$Program].TryAdd($_.docnbr,$_.manual)){ $_ } } } }

data.comment: $CsdbProgram = 'B_IFM', 'CH604PROD', 'CTALPROD', 'LJ4045PROD', 'GXPROD' $query = @' SELECT DISTINCT StateValue, StateName, Remark FROM FiniteStateMachineState '@ $statesPerProgram = [System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary[string, pscustomobject]]::new($CsdbProgram.Count) foreach ($Program in $CsdbProgram) { $connectionInfo = $dbConnections.connections.info | Where-Object -FilterScript { $_.serviceName -match ($Program -replace '_').Substring(0, 2) } | Select-Object -First 1 $sqlClOut = Write-Output "SET SQLFORMAT JSON`n$query" | SQLcl -S "***REMOVED***@$($connectionInfo.hostname):$($connectionInfo.port)/$($connectionInfo.serviceName)" | Join-String -Separator $([Environment]::NewLine) $sqlOutErrSplit = $sqlClOut | Select-String -Pattern '(?ms)(?<json>{.*})(?<err>.*)' | Select-Object -ExpandProperty Matches $sqlOut = $sqlOutErrSplit.Groups['json'].Value | ConvertFrom-Json $states = $sqlOut.results.items $stateNames = [System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary[int, pscustomobject]]::new($states.Count) foreach ($statevalue in $states.statevalue) { $stateNames.Add([int]::Parse($statevalue), ($states | Where-Object { $_.statevalue -eq $statevalue } | Select-Object -ExcludeProperty statevalue)) } $statesPerProgram.Add($Program, $stateNames) }
